parameters: Thief Nora: I-It's so huge! The building is so far away!
Clea: I wonder if they're really wealthy?

Mage Relm: It seems that Caron-sama is using special
techniques to create pearls. Ever since she became the
queen, pearls have become very popular.

Mage Relm: To think that they didn't even spare a glance
before, and now it's all about money!
Clea: I hope this negotiation goes well.

Sophia the priestess: Nobleman Lloyd... also known as the
profligate nobleman.

Priestess Sophia: He is known as the king of the courtesans,
as there is no prostitute in the empire who does not know
him.

Maid: Please refrain from speaking ill of our master. It's
all true, so it brings me a headache of shame and
frustration.

Clea: I hope to meet with Mr. Lloyd. I am Clea from the
Adventurer's Guild, Futera.

Maid Amina: Adventurer's Guild... There are no plans for a
meeting in our master's schedule.

Maid Amina: Please take your leave, or shall I forcefully
escort you out?
Do you challenge me to a fight?
Clea: If it's necessary for the completion of the request.
Maid Amina: I see... I'm not really in the mood, but...
Maid Amina: Shall we do it?

Maid Amina: Welcome back. Next time, please come as a
customer.
Clea: Can you let me through with this?

Maid Amina: Please don't end it on your own. Next, I will
provide you with the best hospitality.
Thief Nora: Eek!? H-He stood up again. What should we do?

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: Well, well, what beautiful young
ladies we have here! Is this a reward from Amina, I wonder!?

Maid Amina: No, they are adventurers who came from the
Adventurer's Guild, my master.
Clea: I came because there's something I want to ask you.

Lewd Aristocrat Luid: I see, I see! For now, come inside and
let's talk, go ahead!

Maid Amina: It's not perfect, but... there's no helping it.
Since all of you have become customers, please come inside.
Clea: Those are the thieves... Let's defeat them all.
Clea: It looks like this is the end.

Aspida Alliance Warrior Captain: I heard a rumor about a
group of four women, including an unusually strong maid...

Aspida Alliance Warrior Captain: That doesn't matter! I will
definitely obtain the crystal for the revival of the Aspida
Alliance!

Aspida Alliance Warrior Captain: Impressive skills...! We
shall make an honorable retreat here...!

Priestess Sophia: The transportation of the crystal was
supposed to be top secret, right?

Clea: I'm also curious about that. It seemed like they knew
about the existence of the crystal.
Thief Nora: D-Did someone tell them...?

Mage Relm: Jumping to conclusions is premature! It might be
referring to a different crystal.

Mage Relm: There might be a crystal used for pearl
cultivation, you know!
Clea: ...Let's report to the guild leader.

Clea (There is a possibility of a traitor in the
Adventurer's Guild... The fate of those who break the three
principles of the guild is already determined...)

Clea (Pointing a sword at someone I know... I don't want to
think about it.)
Will you challenge me to a fight?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then do it)
